{"tid":1128378,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"原來 google 個 Thanos Easter Egg 係防劇透","createTime":"2019-04-27T18:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T18:44:06.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcefd0f6e816e7b932fe9260cd0a1585fc26960","tid":1128378,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"真係估唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n===========<br />\n&bull;Avengers: Endgame sees the aftermath of Thanos' devastating act which saw him wipe out half the population with just a click of his gauntlet-clad fingers<br />\n&bull;Google have created a clever Easter Egg hack which sees search results on Thanos disappear in a similar way to those in Avengers: Infinity War<br />\n&bull;One click of the animated  gauntlet and the individual entries atomise one by one<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12785846-6966301-image-a-1_1556358447662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12785846-6966301-image-a-1_1556358447662.jpg&h=76897c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Evil: Fans flocked to the cinema to see the aftermath of supervillain Thanos' devastating act which saw him wipe out half the population with just a click of his gauntlet-clad fingers<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12785778-6966301-image-a-2_1556358451335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12785778-6966301-image-a-2_1556358451335.jpg&h=8e0c2181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Wow: With the internet awash with Avengers excitement, Google have joined in with the hype and have created a clever Easter Egg for people searching for information on the evil character<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12785814-6966301-image-a-3_1556358472952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12785814-6966301-image-a-3_1556358472952.jpg&h=edc5501f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Marvel-ous! Click on the gauntlet and the magic happens - with the search page disappearing before your eyes in a way that echoes the fate of half of the universe in Avengers: Infinity War<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12785828-6966301-image-a-4_1556358479138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12785828-6966301-image-a-4_1556358479138.jpg&h=138bb92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Vanished: One by one individual entries atomise leaving a blank space, while the countdown displaying the amount of entries begins to plummet, leaving just half the original number<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12785872-6966301-image-a-13_1556358789546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12785872-6966301-image-a-13_1556358789546.jpg&h=26c0abe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Goodbye: The clever search engine hack sees the Google entries disappear in a way similar to Nick Fury and half of the population in the Infinity War film<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785896-6966301-image-m-15_1556359301604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785896-6966301-image-m-15_1556359301604.jpg&h=7d61acab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785884-6966301-image-m-16_1556359311143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785884-6966301-image-m-16_1556359311143.jpg&h=c02ead05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785898-6966301-image-m-17_1556359325303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785898-6966301-image-m-17_1556359325303.jpg&h=d3a5bf62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785902-6966301-image-m-18_1556359337283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785902-6966301-image-m-18_1556359337283.jpg&h=517b6607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785904-6966301-image-m-19_1556359347649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785904-6966301-image-m-19_1556359347649.jpg&h=5136cdeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Amazed: Fans soon rushed to Twitter to share their thoughts on the genius hack, with many heaping it with praise and some even calling it the 'best thing ever'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/23/19/12628262-6951881-image-a-15_1556045934669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F23%2F19%2F12628262-6951881-image-a-15_1556045934669.jpg&h=4489d6b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Big hit: Meanwhile, Avengers: Endgame has broken a box-office record in North America, becoming the first film to gross $140 million in a single day<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/11/12785860-6966301-image-a-20_1556359442663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F11%2F12785860-6966301-image-a-20_1556359442663.jpg&h=ccc45f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Popular: The jaw-dropping sum was made in the 24 hours since the movie opened for preview screenings on Thursday afternoon<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/04/27/10/12628270-6966301-The_movie_could_make_a_potential_all_time_best_of_270_million_to-a-14_1556358836288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F10%2F12628270-6966301-The_movie_could_make_a_potential_all_time_best_of_270_million_to-a-14_1556358836288.jpg&h=075c07bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Success: The Disney and Marvel production toppled the previous record set by 2015's Star Wars: The Force Awakens, which made $119 million in the same market<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/04/27/5961237773316308435/1024x576_MP4_5961237773316308435.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F5961237773316308435%2F1024x576_MP4_5961237773316308435.mp4&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8rO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=233b9bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/04/27/5961237773316308435/1024x576_MP4_5961237773316308435.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/04/26/5605475435782422591/1024x576_MP4_5605475435782422591.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F5605475435782422591%2F1024x576_MP4_5605475435782422591.mp4&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8rO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=6772fa76\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/04/26/5605475435782422591/1024x576_MP4_5605475435782422591.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/03/14/1992530476024285365/1024x576_MP4_1992530476024285365.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F1992530476024285365%2F1024x576_MP4_1992530476024285365.mp4&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8rO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=db138abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/03/14/1992530476024285365/1024x576_MP4_1992530476024285365.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/v